sec.p:
The pro-vitamin A was estimated following our previously described method [7, 14]. The fresh leaf samples (0.5 g each) were extracted with adding acetone (10 mL, 80%) followed by centrifugation for 3–4 min at 10,000 × g. A spectrophotometer was set at 510 nm and 480 nm, respectively to read the absorbance. The results were calculated as mg pro-vitamin A per 100 g FW.
