The antioxidant activity was estimated following the DPPH radical quenching assay [46, 47] and the ABTS method [48]. The absorbance was read at 517 (DPPH) and 734 (ABTS) nm using a Hitachi spectrophotometer (Japan). The antioxidant capacity (ABTS and DPPH) was measured according to the following equation:
